**StreamBladeChart**  
**Description:**  
Renders high-speed numeric streams into a sharp, blade-style scrolling chart for real-time insight.

```markdown
# StreamBladeChart - High-Speed Realtime Visualizer

StreamBladeChart displays live metrics with a focus on smoothness and high refresh performance.

## Features
- Fast real-time updates  
- Optional threshold indicators  
- Built with Matplotlib

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamBladeChart.git
cd StreamBladeChart
python visualize.py
